tables.name: todos
tables.def:
CREATE TABLE `todos` (
  `id` bigint NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `title` longtext,
  `status` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=[Redacted by tbls] DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci
